content: Just went back into the program and the contents of all folders have gone even though it says the messages are there at the top. I exited the program, restarted it and now it appears to be working normally, except for one folder which is still missing over half its emails.

content: Kliknite ľavým tlačidlom myši na priečinok "Odeslaná pošta" a stále držte tlačidlo myši a potiahnite týmto priečinkom a vytiahnite si ho do priestoru kam patrí, alebo kam chcete.
